{"tid":2218244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：保就業有助勞工市場　政府沒要求超市辦抽獎","createTime":"2020-09-26T05:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T06:03:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"766de286c1dda83f441634e69cb02d269a35d1d4","tid":2218244,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:46:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551766-20200926.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551766-20200926.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=57f87a5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551766-20200926.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c4c2c68a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551766-20200926.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光說，「保就業」計劃並不完美，但的確有助勞工市場，又指如非「保就業」計劃，僱員放無薪假的情況會更嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n政府要求連鎖超級市場推出優惠回饋市民，羅致光指沒有要求超市以特定形式回饋，否認政府要求超市舉辦大抽獎，形容是議員冤枉他。"},{"pid":"9624533399ecf5c90b6c9c6171fe97dadd630dad","tid":2218244,"uid":21817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"而家只係嚴重，唔係最嚴重，已經做得叫好好<br />\n政府又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}